IAN'S VISION
This election is about you; your children, your job, your retirement and your future. It is vital that we choose a strong economic recovery, transparency over lies as well as unity over division. After all, Calgary is my home as well as yours, so let's make it the best it can be.
This is what Ian believes in.
A perfect representation of hard working Calgarians...
Father of 3, Husband, Oil and gas worker, Immigrant.
